This section will give an overview of this offering, who is it for (target users), value to the customers and potentially include competitor information or how it is unique.
Azure Center for SAP Solutions is an Azure native offering that makes SAP a top-level workload in Azure. It enables end-customers and service providers to seamlessly deploy or manage their SAP systems on Azure.
With Azure Center for SAP Solutions, you do not have to worry about setting up individual components and connecting them as the create experience provides a guided, catalog-based way to ease the deployment experience. 
Virtual Instances for SAP, which is a logical representation of the resources of an SAP system, simplifies the management of SAP systems and Quality Checks increase the reliability and quality of these systems on Azure.
